中文主页
			





	
		
			
个人简介
			
			<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">牛田野，浙江大学转化医学研究院和附属邵逸夫医院特聘研究员，博士生导师。<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2003<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">年毕业于中国科技大学近代物理系，被授予理学学士学位，并获&ldquo;郭沫若&rdquo;奖学金。同年保送本校物理电子学专业攻读直博，于<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2008<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">年毕业被授予工学博士学位。<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2009<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">年至<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2012<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">年在美国乔治亚理工大学医学物理专业做博士后，从事医学影像引导治疗系统的硬件建设与研究工作。<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2013<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">年在乔治亚理工大学晋升研究员并兼客座助理教授，负责医学影像实验室科研与建设，协助本系构建医学物理实验教学体系。<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2014<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">年起任浙江大学转化医学研究院和附属邵逸夫医院研究员，开展医学物理与工程的教学科研工作。已发表国际一级期刊学术论文<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">20<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">余篇，国际会议报告<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">20<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">余次，拥有美国专利<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">项，研究专利受到医科达和瓦里安等国际一流医疗器械公司关注。近年来担任美国卫生研究所（<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">NIH<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">）项目合作研究员，同时任医学物理领域顶级期刊<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">MedicalPhysics<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">和<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">PhysicsinMedicineandBiology<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">资深审稿人，<spanlang="EN-US"style="font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:
宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">ComputationalandMathematicalMethodsinMedicine<spanstyle="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">期刊客座主编。获一系列研究奖项，包括国际电气电子工程师协会医学影像分会新人奖和美国医学物理学会科学论坛最佳报告。
			
				
			工作研究领域
			
			1）新一代锥形束CT系统性能提升：锥束X射线探测器广泛用于病床边图像引导，但其成像质量受到散射污染等因素影响较差，无法满足定量应用需要。本项目借助数学物理模型估计散射信号并从投影中修正，以改善成像质量。
2）低剂量计算机断层重建：锥束CT在治疗引导中要进行重复扫描，累积剂量较高。为降低高剂量对人体损伤，本项目设计新型CT重建算法，加入数学物理先验信息到重建过程中，在保持成像质量同时抑制辐射剂量。
3）锥束引导的自适应放射治疗：锥束CT的在线监控特性使其适合自适应放射治疗，即根据锥束CT图像在治疗中修正计划，以提高治疗效果。
4）特种锥束CT应用：基于锥束CT核心模块衍生出的各类专用型CT机，如微锥束CT、乳腺锥束CT和移动锥束CT设备等。
			
				
